channel.title: Is there JUST ONE working server...?
channel.description:
I know this might sound strange but I have spent the last hour and a half surfing through the RS2 advertisement server and RS2 server sections trying to find just one that I am able to connect to. Just an hour before that I was able to connect to a few perfectly fine but all of a sudden I can't find any that work.
I have the latest updated java, I have hamachi, I have a pretty fast computer and I have established my port/connection. When I go to the runescape.com website the game works perfectly fine but none of the private servers here work for me :(
Can I get some help?
